```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant WebApp as Web App
    participant Routes as FOV Routes
    participant Validation as Validation Service
    participant FOVService as FOV Service
    participant TLERepo as TLE Repository
    participant PropStrategy as Propagation Strategy
    participant Cache

    User->>WebApp: Request FOV calculation
    WebApp->>Routes: POST /api/fov/calculate
    activate Routes

    Routes->>Validation: Validate request parameters
    activate Validation
    Validation-->>Routes: Validation result
    deactivate Validation

    Routes->>FOVService: Calculate FOV
    activate FOVService

    FOVService->>TLERepo: Get TLE data
    activate TLERepo
    TLERepo->>Cache: Check for cached TLEs
    activate Cache
    Cache-->>TLERepo: Return cached TLEs
    deactivate Cache
    TLERepo-->>FOVService: Return TLE data
    deactivate TLERepo

    FOVService->>PropStrategy: Propagate satellites
    activate PropStrategy
    PropStrategy-->>FOVService: Return positions
    deactivate PropStrategy

    FOVService->>FOVService: Filter by FOV
    FOVService-->>Routes: Return FOV results
    deactivate FOVService

    Routes-->>WebApp: Return HTTP response
    deactivate Routes
    WebApp-->>User: Display results
```
